description: This resource explores the concept of 'Slow AI,' advocating for more inclusive, ethical, and creative approaches to artificial intelligence. It is a community-driven initiative that encourages thoughtful reflection on the future of AI design and implementation.

title: DAIR Institute – Distributed AI Research
description: The DAIR Institute is an independent research organization founded by Timnit Gebru, focused on community-rooted AI research outside of Big Tech. It aims to promote ethical, inclusive, and transparent AI development through independent studies and initiatives.
